reviews.text: Have been here twice in the last couple months and I don't understand the negative reviews.  The food is simple, but certainly isn't terrible.  I've had the fried rice and noodle soup and it was fine.  Kayak rental is very reasonable and I have found the family who runs this place to be very helpful both times.  The old woman really runs the show and kind of bosses her husband around, which is entertaining to watch.
Mini tuck shop with properly priced items available. Owner was nice to speak with. Beach items, light snacks and beverages are available at the store too.
Nice shop that provides tons of water sport equipments like canoes and surfing boards
Lucky if you can an order in. Shambolic. Food was atrocious.
Nice place

同朋友共4人租艇取4支槳，其中一人出發扒了十分鐘後，有支槳甩了一面槳落水，茫茫大海想執都執吾番，還艇時被罰錢500大元。完全無寫明損毀如何計算，只能講係打死狗講價。如果大家想玩水就請小心檢查過用品先好租。
態度不可一世，全心敲詐，無良士多，請比少少良心作業
很難吃!! 不要叫奶荼, 無茶味只有奶穌味!! 又收得貴!! 唔会再幫襯!
態度差 食物同飲品質素太貴 冇人情味
